    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/6e80ee5c87c8fcd756e101beb18f44bb.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“与少女们一起对抗黑暗！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典扫雷游戏的传统目标是精确定位关卡中的每个地雷（黑暗）实例。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与少女们成为朋友，根据关系，她们会为你揭示安全格子或封印黑暗格子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/7cec7384c9e21b83343162157ed2e604.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 10 位拥有独特技能的不同少女将在每场游戏中为您提供帮助</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 与少女互动越多，关系就会越好，她的技能也会变得更强大，对你更有用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 可定制的难度和排行榜，可保存您的最佳成绩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > · 关于少女们背景故事的一些秘密等待着我们去发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.poster.avif?t=1735096262\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.webm?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009500/extras/901feb43a0d5a2409758bc4edf33d95b.mp4?t=1735096262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗已经来临，正试图吞噬一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，少女们想知道，如果黑暗只是想和我们做朋友呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(✿˶◕‿◕˶)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >____________________________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个游戏是由一位独立开发者制作的小型项目，欢迎在商店页面右侧加入Discord并分享你的观点。大陆可以加QQ群769386696。</p>",
